<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Prag</head><p>Der Rat teilt wegen Ulrich Risbeck mit, dass er nicht Bürger zu Nürnberg ist.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_231" id="114r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_231_r3l23">Der Gröʒʒern Stat cʒü Prage </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_231_r3l24"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Riſpecken <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>Laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_231_r3l25">wir ewr vveiſheit wiſſen / daʒ der vnſer <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> nicht ıſt / Vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſein </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_231_line_1575805981731_76">des </ab></add> nicht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_231_r3l26">mechtig ſein / . Alſo / daʒ vvir dar cʒü nichts getün künnen / wo vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_231_r3l27">aber <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erſamkeit / lıeb dienſt vnd <expan>frewntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>beweiſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan> / Des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_231_r3l28"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvir wıllig vnd <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das allcʒeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>vts<ex>upra</ex></expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_231" id="114r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der grözzern stat czü Prage</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Rispecken <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewr weisheit wissen, daz der
                        unser <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> nicht ist und <add>des</add> nicht
                        mechtig sein. Also daz wir dar czü nichts getün künnen. Wo wir aber
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> ersamkeit lieb, dienst und
                                <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan>, des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wir willig
                        und <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das allczeit
                        <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>uts<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
